                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/4507" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-0642</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8512 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">暴风集团万般无奈下的断臂求生</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">BaoFeng Group’s abandonment to survive</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">方慧，卜小凡，陆叶，阎蓓蓓</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">上海大学MBA教育管理中心</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">刘焱</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">暴风集团股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">服务业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">10 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">合并范围；成本法；权益法；暴风集团；暴风智能</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"> Consolidation scope; cost method; equity method; BaoFeng Group; BaoFeng Intelligence</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2019年7月29日，暴风集团发布公告，宣布放弃对旗下子公司暴风智能的优先认购权，从而将暴风智能排除在合并范围之外。暴风智能曾是暴风集团为进军互联网电视业务而重金收购的一家子公司，对暴风集团营业收入的贡献达到近80%，虽然被收购后持续出现亏损，但暴风集团一直未曾将其割舍，此次暴风集团毅然决然挥刀断臂，究竟意欲何为？本案例通过介绍暴风集团将暴风智能排出合并范围及其所产生的相应后果，引导学员思考如何从实质重于形式的原则来判断企业的合并范围，同时学习和掌握排出合并范围后长期股权投资在个别报表和合并报表上的核算及其形成的财务影响。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">On July 29, 2019, the BaoFeng Group issued an announcement announcing that it had waived its right of first subscription to its subsidiary BaoFeng Intelligence, thereby excluding BaoFeng Intelligence from the scope of consolidation. BaoFeng Intelligence was once a subsidiary of the BaoFeng Group, which had been heavily acquired in order to enter the Internet TV business. It contributed nearly 80% to the operating income of the BaoFeng Group. Although it continued to make losses after the acquisition, the BaoFeng Group has never given it up. This time the BaoFeng Group resolutely waved its sword and broken its arm. What is the intention? This case introduces BaoFeng Group to remove BaoFeng Intelligence from the scope of consolidation and its corresponding consequences, and guides students to think about how to judge the scope of a company&#39;s consolidation from the principle of substance over form, while learning and mastering the long-term equity investment Accounting on individual statements and consolidated financial statements and the financial impact of these.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2019</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《财务会计》、《财务报表分析》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">合并范围的判断、对长期股权投资成本法和权益法转换的会计核算</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2020-06</td>
                            </tr>
